## Modified scripts for the brscan-skey application

Differences to the original versions are:

 - scantofile.sh now creates a pdf in the lineart mode instead of a tiff in color mode and now supports ADF
 - scantoimage.sh now creates a pdf in color mode instead of a tiff in color mode and now supports ADF 
 - scantoocr.sh now creates an ocr readable pdf in lineart mode and supports ADF
